en.title: FE Event Manila, 10th January 2009.
en.content:
FE held its 6th Achievers Recognition Dinner in Philippines on 10th Jan 2009 at Gloria Maris Sharkfin Restaurant in Greenhills, Manila. It was an energy packed evening with around 400 Leaders, Members and Invited Guests. Everyone was full of enthusiasm and welcomed each other with New Year greetings! The evening started with the energetic High Street band playing old favorites and current hits. Jeremy Looi, FE's Philippines Country Licensee gave the opening speech and shared his message, emphasizing the importance of seizing the opportunity and staying focus and committed to building the business. Jeremy also took the opportunity to read out FE CEO Paul Ting's dynamic New Year message to all.

Hosting the program is the indefatigable duo of Dr. Anarie Reyes and Efren Fortuna. FE Founder Director K.S. Lee shared about the importance of having the right frame of mind in goal setting. Jimmy Dee, FE leader from Guam, graced the occasion with a couple of songs. Jimmy is also known as the Elvis Presley and Tom Jones of Guam. FE Presidential Director Pastor Art Medina did the Quantum Pendant demonstration for the audience. The crowd roared with excitement as they see the amazing effect of FE's QP. A lifting demonstration was performed and a 76 year old retired civil servant could not believe that he had just lifted a man weighing twice his weight together with three other guys with just his fingers!

VIP guests include Alvin & Cindy Patrimonio with their daughters Clarice and Christine who are professional tennis players together with guests from the national tennis team, Judge Lorenzo Veneracion, Monsour Del Rosario, Dr George & Becky Sarakinis, Mr.& Mrs. Poe Gratela, board of Governors of POEA (Philippine Overseas Employment Agency) and veteran actress Ms. Daisy Romualdez.

Congratulations to all the new Directors and Executive Directors!
